类 NativeToJsMessageQueue

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.cordova.NativeToJsMessageQueue

  • public class NativeToJsMessageQueue
extends java.lang.Object
    Holds the list of messages to be sent to the WebView.

      Uses webView.evaluateJavascript to execute messages.
      static class  NativeToJsMessageQueue.LoadUrlBridgeMode
      Uses webView.loadUrl("javascript:") to execute messages.
      static class  NativeToJsMessageQueue.NoOpBridgeMode
      Uses JS polls for messages on a timer..
      static class  NativeToJsMessageQueue.OnlineEventsBridgeMode
      Uses online/offline events to tell the JS when to poll for messages.
